Jessalyn Van Trump https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jessalyn_Van_Trump 0 Jessalyn Van Trump (January 16, 1887 – May 2, 1939) was an American silent film actress. She appeared in over eighty films between 1911 and 1928. In the early 1910s she often appeared opposite Pauline Bush.
